g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都明<br />\n可能朝早去完lecture，晏晝去集會<br />\n唔返晏晝堂<br />\n<br />\n長罷不了<br />\n利申：夢我有發，但係罷工罷課我唔太過到自己嗰關<br />\n我本身已經遲咗年，唔想再追唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50a37093063d27fe7dd5297e9bb310b40eab6b5","tid":1516731,"uid":247699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=d0ee105b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0d876296067e92e13c2143e2bab23ac156c33c","tid":1516731,"uid":255896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79d87d70bc28be4f3d22d4a313756c6df4550a8","tid":1516731,"uid":27243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"嗰日講後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都明<br />\n可能朝早去完lecture，晏晝去集會<br />\n唔返晏晝堂<br />\n<br />\n長罷不了<br />\n利申：夢我有發，但係罷工罷課我唔太過到自己嗰關<br />\n我本身已經遲咗年，唔想再追唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"我都淨係罷2,3號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68781431749149ec6f238a5030fc0c0e9c16bd89","tid":1516731,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da00d15cead9862d186d44e42eb7ca709a6bf8c0","tid":1516731,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8b53816dd88f434c86f916b646b213a5401fc4e7","tid":1516731,"uid":27243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae0d876296067e92e13c2143e2bab23ac156c33c","tid":1516731,"uid":255896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79d87d70bc28be4f3d22d4a313756c6df4550a8","tid":1516731,"uid":27243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"嗰日講後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都明<br />\n可能朝早去完lecture，晏晝去集會<br />\n唔返晏晝堂<br />\n<br />\n長罷不了<br />\n利申：夢我有發，但係罷工罷課我唔太過到自己嗰關<br />\n我本身已經遲咗年，唔想再追唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"我都淨係罷2,3號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢J<br />\n認真，讀U最多defer，asshole無就無"},{"pid":"0af18cffbbf3c5b2b4328e39633870a578b985db","tid":1516731,"uid":308486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bffdc8afc1fd7976fdb33c7caef40db7a35c0d1c","tid":1516731,"uid":255896,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"我讀商科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}